  ('optometrist-moex-02291', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-108-c33a0f9f', 'sub-optometrist-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '進行視網膜檢影後測出來的度數不盡理想，先將散光度數移除並把眼睛霧視至20/40左右，同時選用散光 鐘面圖（clock dial chart）檢測。此時患者表示十二點鐘與一點鐘中間的線條顏色最深最明顯，若您以負 圓柱透鏡矯正，散光軸度應放在幾度？', '["15度", "75度", "105度", "165度"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:52+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "29132c54255c", "answer_pdf_sha1": "4ae5d106f009", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108110", "c": "112", "s": "1103", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視光學", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、108年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 21, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-02292', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-108-c33a0f9f', 'sub-optometrist-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何種雙眼平衡的檢查方法，兩眼的影像是完全分離？', '["連續交替遮蓋法（successive alternate occlusion）", "隔板法／TIB法（septum/Turville''s infinity balance）", "偏光立體影像法（Polaroid/vectograph）", "漢佛萊斯法（Humphriss method）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:52+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "29132c54255c", "answer_pdf_sha1": "4ae5d106f009", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108110", "c": "112", "s": "1103", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視光學", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、108年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 22, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-02293', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-108-c33a0f9f', 'sub-optometrist-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '操作裂孔板驗光（stenopaic slit refraction）檢查時，被檢眼在裂孔40度角方向矯正視力為0.6，度數為-1.75 D； 在裂孔110度角方向矯正視力為0.8，度數為-2.50 D，此時裂孔板落焦在眼內與矯正鏡片度數的敘述，下 列何者正確？', '["眼內20度角焦線比130度角焦線更靠近視網膜", "眼內130度角焦線比20度角焦線更靠近視網膜", "矯正鏡片度數為-1.75DC×040與-2.50DC×110", "矯正鏡片度數為-1.75DS/-0.75DC×040"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:52+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "29132c54255c", "answer_pdf_sha1": "4ae5d106f009", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108110", "c": "112", "s": "1103", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視光學", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、108年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 23, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL)
